<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_2fbfd534-6c6c-47d0-b87d-62dd6ad1a3f8" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>10.2.3</sptc><title id="_843e716e-f222-442e-a368-69ce41028e27">Area outside shower area</title><archive-num>2019: Table 3.8.1.1</archive-num><subclause id="_07b07b6e-a476-46eb-b4da-46413ca41d31" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_314f5bc2-b403-4f2b-9e13-d030ef9258b4">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>For concrete, compressed fibre-cement and fibre-cement sheet flooring, the floor of the room must be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1520_0.5.0.xml#_787642fb-810b-4dc9-8ea9-f54fcfbc19e1" id="_d7c495ba-144e-4fed-ba06-b93dee2459c4" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">water resistant</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_a954ec60-f6ff-44b9-97a8-2bc077bd6bac" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2bffedb0-0592-4723-8fa9-e351b29fb88e">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>For timber floors including particleboard, plywood and other timber based flooring materials, the floor of the room must be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1519_0.5.0.xml#_02296d09-c6a7-41f4-a398-1f059045818c" id="_d1981de9-b5d5-4a51-b3b5-32233caa6186" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">waterproof</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_e09a3803-cb02-4213-8683-8c550c5c9699" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_554aa357-8c2f-4993-85cc-647250451284">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>Wall/floor junctions must be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_182e21d4-1982-4926-ae4b-75158cbd40ad"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1519_0.5.0.xml#_02296d09-c6a7-41f4-a398-1f059045818c" id="_678a2d79-14db-4722-9b48-ded2585ed936" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">waterproof</xref>; and</li><li id="_cfadb9ed-a3c6-44e9-935f-11f8ce6abfb1">where a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1305_0.16.0.xml#_f3cdd6b2-0801-4750-ac8b-515dde29def5" id="_0044cb85-871a-41f7-aedb-0cf78c4b9fbb" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">flashing</xref> is used, the horizontal leg must be not less than 40 mm.</li></ol></subclause></clause>